description: This skill is a built in Hokie Ambassador designed to help answer questions from Virginia Tech students-- primarily new or freshman students. The Hokie Helper can tell you where to find resources at Virginia Tech. Resources range from where to find good hiking locations or where to study to resources at Virginia Tech and abroad for illness, anxiety, suicide, and sexual assault.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Hokie Helper where can I go hiking?
Alexa tell Hokie Helper I feel sick.
name: Hokie Helper
shortDescription: A Hokie Ambassador designed to answer questions from Virginia Tech students.
